          <div type="advert" colSpan="2" xml:id="deg-ad-bur01">
              <head>BURMAN'S Celebrated CLIPPERS</head>
              <p>FOR BARBERS, HORSES AND DOGS</p>
              <p>THE BURMAN POWER CLIPPER No. 8.</p>
              <p>WITH WRIST JOINT.</p>
              <p>As supplied to the Tsar of Russia, the King of Denmark, the Duke of
                  Conriaught, &amp;c.</p>
              <p>For beauty of design and superiority of workmanship the Burman Power Clippers
                  stand supreme and unassailable.</p>
              <p>The "Warwick" Clipper. Cuts over three teeth.</p>
              <p>FOR SMALL STABLES.</p>
              <p>The BURMAN No. 5.</p>
              <p>WITH STAND. </p>
              <p>Strong and Reliable.</p>
              <p>Every Machine Warranted.</p>
              <p>Despatch Hair Clipper</p>
              <p>Made in 3 sizes.</p>
              <p>BURMAN &amp; Sons, Ld., Lee Bank Works; Birmingham, ENGLAND.</p>
          </div>
